      • Drill3484

        public void Drill3484()
               throws Exception
        This test is not checking results because the bug fixed only appears with functions taking no arguments. I could alternatively use something like the now() function, but this still would be hard to write result verification for. The important aspect of the test is that it verifies that the previous IOOB does not occur. The various no-argument functions should be verified in other ways.
